welcome_message_title: Welcome to New Port Richey East
welcome_message_body: "Welcome to New Port Richey East, the charming city known for its beautiful beaches and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that this vibrant destination has to offer. Have a wonderful stay!"
